WEBVTT

00:00:01.692 --> 00:00:06.107
Há duas semanas, procurei a palavra
"nacionalista" no Twitter.

00:00:06.109 --> 00:00:07.980
Os resultados foram bem empolgantes,

00:00:07.980 --> 00:00:11.347
com expressões como,
"racista idiota entusiasmado",

00:00:11.351 --> 00:00:12.401
(Risos)

00:00:12.401 --> 00:00:14.550
"supremacista branco idiota",

00:00:14.550 --> 00:00:16.500
"fantoches fascistas",

00:00:16.504 --> 00:00:17.592
(Risos)

00:00:17.592 --> 00:00:20.379
"Orwelliano, hitleriano, assustador".

00:00:20.379 --> 00:00:22.570
Então procurei a palavra "globalista"

00:00:22.570 --> 00:00:25.816
e obtive coisas como,
"socialistas traidores",

00:00:25.816 --> 00:00:28.790
"propaganda corporativa nojenta",

00:00:28.790 --> 00:00:31.819
"líderes financeiros elitistas",